         <span class="text-primary">3. Color Picker </span>   
         : Provides a color picker which saves a lot of time just press <code>ctrl+E</code> to open the quick edit
         </p>
        </div>
        
         <div class="row text-center">         
           <img  src="${pageContext.request.contextPath}/images/color-edit.JPG"></img>       
